{{Unlicensed}}'''Kronus''' was a thug from the planet [[Mandrine/Legends|Mandrine]]. He and his goons were known to have caused a brawl in a bar called [[Maizie's]] while [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Scarlet Bloodhawk]] was visiting. He was killed when one of his dupes drew a [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] who was then shot. The detonator was then picked up by [[Tyric (Shaliz'Na)|Tyric]] and thrown at Kronus. They were scraping his remains for weeks.

